data.description: SELLERS OFFERING a $5,000 allowance for closing costs, etc!  Welcome home to this lovely ranch within walking distance of schools, Community Center, pool, dog park, ballfields and a beautiful park!  Walk in to the large living room with all new luxury vinyl flooring, cozy fireplace and built in desk area.  Kitchen has brand new countertops and all SS appliances are only 2-5 years old.  Step down into a HUGE family room perfect for gatherings and access to the patio and fully fenced in backyard.  The main floor has three bedrooms with original wood floors but Sellers have ample new flooring left over to finish all three!  The basement has been recently finished with laundry, sitting area in what Sellers are now using as the fourth bedroom with closet and connected 3/4 bath!  New roof and gutters in 2023, all new windows in 2022.  Spacious off street parking as well!  Come see this one!
